{"article_id":"bbxsOl1tPhWT84AB","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump escalated the feud between himself and his own attorney general Friday ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"firing back at Jeff Sessions with a series of tweets","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"seeming to mock Sessions","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"for not investigating his opponents .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"The president pleaded for a number of investigations","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"and quoted a statement","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"offered by Sessions on Thursday ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"in which the attorney general defended the Justice Department","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"it would n't be influenced by politics .","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"`` 'Department of Justice will not be improperly influenced by political considerations . ' Jeff , this is GREAT , what everyone wants ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"so look into all of the corruption on the 'other side '","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"including deleted Emails , Comey lies & leaks , Mueller conflicts , McCabe , Strzok , Page , Ohr , ''","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"the president posted early Friday .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"He continued listing off others","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"who","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"he believes","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"Sessions should investigate in another tweet","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"and offered another request :","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"`` Open up the papers & documents","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"without redaction ?","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Come on Jeff ,","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"you can do it ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"the country is waiting ! ''","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"The mention of documents and redactions is an apparent reference to Trump 's wish","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"that the FISA surveillance warrants of his former aide Carter Page be declassified and released","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"without redactions .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"Attorney General Jeff Sessions defends himself","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"- again -","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"in face of attacks from President Trump","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"House Republicans have requested the measure ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"but the White House has yet to get involved in the matter .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"In another tweet , Trump also pointed to the Justice Department 's sentencing a former U.S. intelligence contractor to 63 months for leaking information about Russian meddling .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"Trump said","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"this was `` small potatoes ''","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"compared to Hillary Clinton .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"In a Fox News interview","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that aired Thursday ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"the president suggested","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"he might release the material after the midterm elections .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"`` At the right time , I think","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"I 'm going to have to do the documents .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"I did n't want to .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"But I think","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"I 'm going to have to , ''","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"`` There 's such corruption . ''","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"It 's not new for Trump to rail against Sessions .","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"The two have had a tumultuous relationship since Sessions ' decision","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"to recuse himself from heading the investigation into Russian meddling in the 2016 presidential election .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"But matters escalated this week with the conviction of former Trump campaign chairman Paul Manafort and the guilty plea","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"entered by former Trump attorney and fixer Michael Cohen .","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"Sessions issued a statement Thursday","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"his office would `` not be improperly influenced by political considerations ''","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"just hours after the airing of the Fox interview","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"where the president railed against Sessions .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"When asked ,","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"Trump did n't dismiss the notion","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"of firing the attorney general .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":123,"left":0,"right":122,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":122,"left":109,"right":121,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":88,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":65,"right":87,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":1,"right":64,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":2,"right":63,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":84,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":74,"right":83,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":70,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":5,"right":69,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":69,"left":66,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":8,"right":67,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":67,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":73,"left":72,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":11,"right":71,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":71,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":77,"right":82,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":77